OT="";
for(j=0;j<MI.length;j++){
OT+=ML.charAt(MI.charCodeAt(j)-48);
}document.write(OT);
// --></script></p>
<p>I get a ton of email, so if I don’t respond it doesn’t mean that I haven’t looked at your work or read your email. I look at all emails, it’s just hard to respond to every­one. And if you can, please keep the email short. Thanks!</p>
</p>
